data.description: Welcome to the epitome of countryside living! Located in Athens, Tennessee, this stunning property is a haven of peace and tranquility. Enjoy the deer, sunset, and mountain views on 5 acres of land. With gorgeous, vaulted wood paneled ceilings, wood beams, and quaint brick walled kitchen - this newer home exudes old farmhouse charm. 3 Bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms with recently renovated master bathroom.  Walk in closet in master bedroom has been extended providing ample storage. Brand new windows 2021, new water heater 2022.  Ductwork under home was updated in 2020 to provide better efficiency.  Fenced back yard. This property is truly a dream come true, combining a peaceful country setting with generous living areas and modern conveniences!  Athens is nicknamed 'the friendly city' and is nestled between Chattanooga and Knoxville.  This home is close to the interstate; however, Athens offers many activities such as festivals, an art center, parks, and outdoor trails. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful home yours!
